  "name": "genesis-field-canonical-form",
  "spec_section": "1.11",
  "description": "JCS lex-slotting of the OPTIONAL delegation_cert_hash genesis field. Two genesis records identical except for the field: the with-field canonical form slots delegation_cert_hash between creator_key (c-r) and event_type (e); the without-field form omits it entirely (never null). Presence/absence changes the canonical bytes, so the two records carry DISTINCT signatures and DISTINCT record hashes. Records that omit the field are byte-identical to pre-delegation output.",
